<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL26">
<l>pōtellām pōtu koṇṭuṉ poṉṉaṭi puṉaiya māṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>tītilā moḻikaḷ koṇṭuṉ tirukkuṇañ ceppa māṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>kātalāl neñca maṉpu kalantilē ṉatutaṉ ṉālē</l>
<l>ētilē ṉaraṅkark kellē eṉceyvāṉ tōṉṟi ṉēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I do not adorn Your golden feet with flowers at all times.</l>
<l>I do not utter Your sacred qualities with blemishless words.</l>
<l>I have not blended affection [deriving] from love to [my] heart.</l>
<l>Because of that I am a stranger to Him of Raṅgam.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, what have I been born for?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
